Package de.weltraumschaf.juberblog.template

Helper classes for templating.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Assignable
    Implementors can a variable get assigned.
    Renderable
    Implementors can render them self to a string.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Configurations
    Factory to create template configurations.
    Freemarker
    Helper to wrap Freemarker.
    Layout
    Extends the template to provide a two step layout.
    Layout.DefaultContent
    Used as a default template which does only contains a string.
    Template
    Template class which encapsulates Freemarker.
